<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CamHub | Private Access</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #000;
            color: #0f0;
            font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        .glitch-header {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #fff;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px #f00, -2px -2px #0f0;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .item-card {
            border: 1px solid #0f0;
            padding: 15px;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.05);
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .item-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px #0f0;
            background: rgba(0, 255, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .price-tag {
            color: #ff0000;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        button {
            background-color: #0f0;
            color: #000;
            border: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        button:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
            background-color: #fff;
        }
        .footer-note {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.8em;
            color: #555;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="glitch-header">CamHub / Магазин</div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="item-card">
            <h3>1 ОНЛАЙН-КАМЕРА 👁️</h3>
            <p>Рандомная точка. Вечный доступ.</p>
            <div class="price-tag">119 ₴</div>
            <button onclick="Telegram.WebApp.sendData('buy_1')">КУПИТЬ ДОСТУП</button>
        </div>

        <div class="item-card" style="border-color: #ff0000;">
            <h3>3 ОНЛАЙН-КАМЕРЫ 🔥</h3>
            <p>Пакет "Наблюдатель".</p>
            <div class="price-tag">299 ₴</div>
            <button style="background-color: #ff0000; color: #fff;" onclick="Telegram.WebApp.sendData('buy_3')">ВЗЯТЬ ОПТОМ</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">SYSTEM I.S.-1 // SECURED ACCESS</div>

    <script src="https://telegram.org/js/telegram-web-app.js"></script>
    <script>
        const webapp = window.Telegram.WebApp;
        webapp.expand();
    </script>
</body>
</html>